{"tid":2238601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青島確診3宗無症狀武漢肺炎感染　一人為的士司機","createTime":"2020-10-11T09:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T09:56:32.000Z","uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0a3a9791caf12898b76ae0d3db43122248c49d","tid":2238601,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20201011/s00004/1602401980356/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e9%9d%92%e5%b3%b6%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba3%e5%ae%97%e7%84%a1%e7%97%87%e7%8b%80%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93-%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%ba%e7%82%ba%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e5%8f%b8%e6%a9%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20201011%2Fs00004%2F1602401980356%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b3%25b6%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba3%25e5%25ae%2597%25e7%2584%25a1%25e7%2597%2587%25e7%258b%2580%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2582%25ba%25e7%259a%2584%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e5%258f%25b8%25e6%25a9%259f&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlUzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=e9313287\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20201011%2Fs00004%2F1602401980356%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b3%25b6%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba3%25e5%25ae%2597%25e7%2584%25a1%25e7%2597%2587%25e7%258b%2580%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2582%25ba%25e7%259a%2584%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e5%258f%25b8%25e6%25a9%259f&h=855e09cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20201011/s00004/1602401980356/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e9%9d%92%e5%b3%b6%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba3%e5%ae%97%e7%84%a1%e7%97%87%e7%8b%80%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93-%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%ba%e7%82%ba%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e5%8f%b8%e6%a9%9f</a><br />\n<br />\n青島市衛健委官網通報，該市今日（11日）新增3宗新冠病毒肺炎無症狀感染，其中兩宗為醫院在對普通就診患者進行核酸檢測時發現，1宗在對排查出的密切接觸者進行即時核酸檢測時發現。<br />\n<br />\n三名確診者為兩男一女，年齡介乎53至58歲。其中韓姓男子9月9日因肺結核病在青島市胸科醫院住院治療，10月4日出院，10日上午到青島市中心醫院做核酸檢測，結果為陽性；11日市疾控中心核酸複檢陽性，確定他為無症狀感染者，轉送定點醫院隔離觀察。<br />\n<br />\n另一名患者為江姓女子，在青島市胸科醫院從事陪護工作。她的丈夫、邵姓男子為的士司機，10月10日上午因出現輕微腦梗症狀到青島市中心醫院急診科就診，核酸檢測結果為陽性。邵姓男子表示開的士時一直有戴口罩，並沒與乘客交談。<br />\n<br />\n青島市已啟動應急響應，開展流行病學調查，對所有排查到的密切接觸者及相關人等即時開展核酸檢測。對3名確診者居住的樓宇、市胸科醫院、市中心醫院急診科等場所全封閉管控和消毒。<br />\n（青島市衛健委網站）"},{"pid":"46af51cb0b847a25cc56ebb4c7d1ad4714a25983","tid":2238601,"uid":103050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8759fc6c1eb43392ea152410ad7edac36baacb","tid":2238601,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">國安法</span></span>"},{"pid":"77dd4b4f6cb7e57ff156006641555f198dd8be7e","tid":2238601,"uid":53922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:25:07.000Z","msg":"新冠病毒肺炎無症狀感染 = 武漢肺炎確診"},{"pid":"362b393d1f038f921f355080efab7f5fa0316859","tid":2238601,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"無症狀唔計"},{"pid":"e2fd2f4d07931132ce05c472a535eed5b5e3d599","tid":2238601,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"冇可能 有晒健康碼乜乜七七"},{"pid":"ba9f56cdd197c9a3486417daaf0600b8c13a1e3c","tid":2238601,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e2fd2f4d07931132ce05c472a535eed5b5e3d599","tid":2238601,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"冇可能 有晒健康碼乜乜七七"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"你呃我唔到"},{"pid":"4a1d05a41295181dd775c4594d41443cf7ff1e64","tid":2